</section>
</section>
<section>
<section id="slide-org307fba2">
<h2 id="org307fba2">What can we conclude?</h2>
<ul>
<li>Non-market sources of income matter</li>
<li>Recent inequality caused by labor income, top 1%</li>
<li>Capital gains matter</li>
<li>Unresolved: How has capital ownership changed since the last recession?</li>

</ul>
</section>
